keyMappings:
map <c-o> goBack
map <c-i> goForward

map J nextTab
map K previousTab
map <c-J> moveTabRight
map <c-K> moveTabLeft
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
g: https://www.google.co.jp/search?q=%s Google
d: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s DuckDuckGo
